 This contains a mini kernel for the RI-MP2 OpenMP
 Fortran code by Buu Pham.
 Updated by JaeHyuk Kwack(jkwack@anl.gov).

 1. Submit an interactive job:
    $ bsub -P TRN006 -nnodes 1 -W 120 -Is /bin/bash

 2. Load modules and build the executables
    $ source source_me_OLCF_ASCENT #or source source_me_OLCF_SUMMIT
    $ make clean; make all

 3. Run the case
    $ ./run_my_rimp2_OLCF.sh


